The paper also discusses the importance of presentation context, which is related to Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper deals with a dataset of real e-commerce users, which could be relevant to the Cybersecurity (cs.CY) category. Finally, the paper involves experiments and data analysis, which could be relevant to the Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) category.
